What is the component of Spring MVC app ?

 -Configure web.xml => where to tell to a servelet container
 	which servlet I am going to deploy
 	<servlet> and defining config file location
 	<servlet-mapping>
 	
 Configure our servlet config file(beans configuration file) => xml file
 	containing beans used by the applications
 	add mvc namespace
 	specify annotation driven and we need to tell spring that he needs to scan project to find annotation
 	add context namespace and add context:component-scan by specifying the package to scan
 	
 - Create controller(s)
 	controller(s) provide(s) methods
 
 - Create view(s)
 	different views technologies :jsp, 
 
 - adding view resolver in the spring beans configuration file=> Concrete 
 	implementation of ViewResolver depending of the situation

- To run the application,we need a servlet container=> Tomcat for example 

Spring Form tag
	spring-form.tld : <%@ taglib prefix="form" uri="http://www.springframework.org/tags/form" %>  
	Some uses
		Evaluates erros
		Set themes
		Deliver internationalized messages
		
	Tags
		checkbox, checboxes
		errors
		form
		hidden
		input
		label
		option,options
	add library access to your jsp page